name: Moonlit Mirage
effect: Increases all party members' Max HP by 30% for 300s. In Co-Op Mode, this effect only applies to your own character(s).
description: Columbina's specialty. The translucent candy looks like droplets of dew gathered from moonlight. Its delicate sweetness flits in and out of reach, as if luring you into a beautiful, fleeting dream. You can't help but wonder at the skill and care that went into making it...
